~ start
if GlobalVariables.haskey == false:
	The door is locked. I tried shoving the door and see if I can use Blackout to break in, but it doesn't budge. I can't get in.
if GlobalVariables.haskey == true:
	do sfx_success()
	The key I got from the roof of the storeroom fits perfectly! I can get in here now.
	set GlobalVariables.town_room = "door"
	do CutsceneManager.new_room("res://scenes/rooms/town_tavern.tscn")
do CutsceneManager.endcutscene()
=> END